{"tid":897507,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"吳京《戰狼2》奪百花影帝","createTime":"2018-11-11T03:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-13T09:35:35.000Z","uid":41343,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ccb9ef7159498ecdf581375a2b80ca5da46e1d83","tid":897507,"uid":41343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T03:27:12.000Z","msg":"內地動作男星吳京憑《戰狼2》榮獲《第34屆大眾電影百花獎》的最佳男主角，他領獎時說：「我是佛山金雞百花的形象大使吳京，這對我本來就是殊榮。以為獲獎沒我啥事了，沒想到能拿獎。觀眾你們給《戰狼2》的榮譽，我誠惶誠恐，會繼續拍好的作品回饋大家。」最後他以大使的身份說：「佛山金雞百花，觀迎您！」作結語，果然盡責。<br />\n<br />\n香港名導林超賢在《第34屆大眾電影百花獎》中憑電影《紅海行動》及《湄公河行動》獲提名最佳導演，雖然自己打自己，但他最終憑《紅》脫穎而出，在101票中以73票大比數擊敗其他對手。他領獎時先以廣東話打招呼，接着以普通話說：「說國語我很擔心，我還記得電影在春節上映時，票房讓團隊的壓力非常大。幸好于老闆（于冬）和（蛟龍）小分隊一直鼓勵我，我們一起往前衝，走到了今天。」他又感謝演員，笑言不知道他們會否肯接他的下一部戲，又多謝工作人員無懼地完成這部電影，同時感謝已相識十多年的朋友兼監製，一直幫助他。 <br />\n<br />\n此外，《第34屆大眾電影百花獎》的最佳影片由《紅海行動》奪得，成為全晚的大贏家，先後包攬最佳新人、最佳女配、最佳男配、最佳導演及最佳影片五個殊榮。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181110/mobile/bkn-20181110213426716-1110_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181110%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181110213426716-1110_00862_001.html&d=fWDTv%2FdfIQUuWDzsGBvUNUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=14ab2549\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181110/mobile/bkn-20181110213426716-1110_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181110/mobile/bkn-20181110210009755-1110_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181110%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181110210009755-1110_00862_001.html&d=fWDTv%2FdfIQUuWDzsGBvUNUzHknCl6yzZyFDyfiap5zU%3D&h=4245003d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181110/mobile/bkn-20181110210009755-1110_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"a184c761779da62f41dca69c225cdc855db75a97","tid":897507,"uid":49391,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-11T05:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8sFdYuf.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8sFdYuf.gif&h=753f0ad6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b5135baf1871a6d250c163ab8adae5f65c787fd3","tid":897507,"uid":124450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T05:39:36.000Z","msg":"百花可以取代金像了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9c5f3a2e945833ffa493435c3d9657b527603a2","tid":897507,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-13T09:35:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}